
HOW TO BUILD AND INSTALL TCRUND
===============================

Dependencies
~~~~~~~~~~~~

cmake    >= 2.6.0	- http://www.cmake.org
libevent >= 1.4.3	- http://monkey.org/~provos/libevent/
xmlrpc-c >= 1.06.27	- http://xmlrpc-c.sf.net

plus the usual build essential components (make, gcc, glibc headers
and so on)


Compilation
~~~~~~~~~~~

$ cmake .
$ make
# make install

Troubleshooting
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* CMake doesn't find includes/libraries
  --------------------------------------

WRITEME

